. He begins to meddle with the lives of everyone in the household and, once his plots are underway, learns there is nothing wrong with his leg. He bribes the doctor and resumes control of the household.',112,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYmMyMTQ2YmItY2YzNi00Y2U0LTljNmQtNWU5NGViMGUyM2NmXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTY5Nzc4MDY@.jpg',1942,'Comedy, Romance','English, French','William Keighley','Julius J. Epstein, Philip G. Epstein, George S. Kaufman, Moss Hart','Jack Saper, Jerry Wald, Hal B. Wallis, Jack L. Warner','Friedrich Hollaender','Tony Gaudio','Jack Killifer'),('The Little Foxes',7.9,'The ruthless, moneyed Hubbard clan lives in, and poisons, their part of the deep South at the turn of the 20th century. Regina Giddens née Hubbard has her daughter under her thumb. Mrs Giddens is estranged from her husband, who is convalescing in Baltimore and suffers from a terminal illness. But she needs him home, and will manipulate her daughter to help bring him back. She has a sneaky business deal that she\'s cooking up with her two elder brothers, Oscar and Ben. Oscar has a flighty, unhappy wife and a dishonest worm of a son. Will the daughter have to marry this contemptible cousin? Who will she grow up to be - her mother or her aunt? Or can she escape the fate of both?',116,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzdkYjU3ZmEtNDZkZS00ZTY5LTgzZDYtNzdiY2ZlOTg5ZDQ5XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc0MzMzNjA@.jpg',1941,'Drama, Romance','English','William Wyler','Lillian Hellman, Lillian Hellman, Arthur Kober, Dorothy Parker, Alan Campbell','Samuel Goldwyn','Meredith Willson','Gregg Toland','Daniel Mandell'),('The Bride Came C.O.D.',6.9,'Oil heiress Joan is going to elope with bandleader Allen whom she\'s known four days. Out-of-money pilot Steve is going to fly them to Nevada but makes a deal with her father to deliver her home unmarried. He flies off with her, an apparent kidnaping, but is forced down in the desert. The bandleader arrives with a preacher, but their marriage (in California, not 