d by the Communist Chinese as spy. Jane Hoyt asks shady shipping magnate Hank Lee for his help but Hank tries to dissuade her from venturing into Red China. Desperate, Jane asks another local, Fernand Rocha, for his help and pays him money. After dishonest and sleazy charlatan Rocha spends her money and forcibly confines her, Hank Lee finally takes pity on her and decides to go searching for her husband himself. Illegally entering Red China Hank finds plenty of trouble.',96,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDcyYzA2NGItYzNlOS00NzY0LWEzZmUtMzIxYjQxNWYzODRkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTU3MTY2Mg@@.jpg',1955,'Adventure, Crime, Drama, Romance, Thriller','English','Edward Dmytryk','Ernest K. Gann, Ernest K. Gann','Buddy Adler','Hugo Friedhofer','Leo Tover','Dorothy Spencer'),('Betrayed',6.3,'A woman starts work on a farm, and gets to know the owner. They get on well, and she also gets on with his children. He asks her to stay on when the work is finished. Things are not what they seem, and we discover the woman is actually an FBI agent...',127,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzFjZjllY2UtNWU5Mi00ZWExLTlkOTItYmJjYjhhMTg2OGY2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjMwMjk0MTQ@.jpg',1988,'Crime, Drama, Thriller','English','Costa-Gavras','Joe Eszterhas','Joe Eszterhas, Hal W. Polaire, Irwin Winkler','Bill Conti','Patrick Blossier','Joële Van Effenterre'),('Mogambo',6.6,'Victor Marswell runs a big game trapping company in Kenya. Eloise Kelly is ditched there, and an immediate attraction happens between them. Then Mr. and Mrs. Nordley show up for their gorilla documenting safari. Mrs. Nordley is not infatuated with her husband any more, and takes a liking to Marswell. The two men and two women have some difficulty arranging these emotions to their mutual satisfaction, but eventually succeed.',116,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzIxMTI3ZTEtMmQzNi00ZWE0LTk4YmYtMzE1MWFmODc0ZDIzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTkxMzEwMzU@.jpg',1953,'Adventure, Drama, Romance','English','John Ford','John Lee Mahin, Wilson Col