elp their child; however, when science fails, they resort to religion. Now, with the Vatican\'s reluctant consent, Bowdern must face the unholy entity that possesses Robbie and perform the first documented exorcism in America. But, the dark enemy is powerful, and he\'ll use Father William\'s inner fears against him. Can the conflicted priest cast out the demon, and save not only the boy\'s life but also his very soul?',110,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMDYxY2Y2ZTMtMWYxZC00Y2I4LTkyOGQtMWE5Zjc1MTdlOGYxL2ltYWdlL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQxNzMzNDI@.jpg',2000,'Horror, Drama','English','Steven E. de Souza','Thomas B. Allen, Michael Lazarou, Steven E. de Souza','Jeri Barchilon, Jane Bartelme, Barbara Title','John Frizzell','Edward J. Pei','Anthony Redman'),('Hell Divers',6.4,'Rival fighter-pilots train in the art of dive bombing while teasing each other about their bravery and manliness. They wind up stranded and must work together for a common goal.',109,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOWJhYzJhOTYtOGFkYi00ZWE2LTg0ZGItYzRiOTY1YmU3ZmFjXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjQzNDI3NzY@.jpg',1931,'Adventure, Drama, Romance','English','George W. Hill','Frank Wead, Harvey Gates, Malcolm Stuart Boylan, James Kevin McGuinness, Ralph Graves, James Warner Bellah, Charles MacArthur, Edward Dean Sullivan','George W. Hill',NULL,'Harold Wenstrom, Harold Lipstein','Blanche Sewell'),('Susan Lenox',NULL,NULL,NULL,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOWJjYjI3MGMtN2QxMC00YjM5LTlkYmYtYmFkZWFkZDQ5MjQyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc0MzMzNjA@.jpg',1931,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('Sporting Blood',6,'Valued thoroughbred mare Southern Queen slips and falls in a mud puddle, breaking her leg. Before she is destroyed, she gives birth to Tommy Boy, who becomes the favorite of his owner, horse breeder Jim Rellence. Ultimately a reluctant Rellence is forced to sell the one-year old to a prominent sportsman, and Tommy enters the world of high stakes racing. He goes through a variety of owners, all of