ack soldier is killed while returning to his base in the deep south. The white people of the area are suspected at first. A tough black army attorney is brought in to find out the truth. We find out a bit more about the dead soldier in flashbacks - and that he was unpopular. Will the attorney find the killer ?',101,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzUxMjY2MWQtNGUyZC00NjkzLWE1MWUtYTM5YzFiZDU5MDM4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNTI4MjkwNjA@.jpg',1984,'Crime, Drama, Mystery, War','English','Norman Jewison','Charles Fuller, Charles Fuller','Norman Jewison, Charles Milhaupt, Patrick J. Palmer, Chiz Schultz, Ronald L. Schwary','Herbie Hancock','Russell Boyd','Caroline Biggerstaff, Mark Warner'),('License to Kill',5.5,'A grieving family whose daughter was killed in a car crash with a drunken driver is outraged and frustrated as they encounter the inevitable bureaucratic delays in bringing the case to trial. Once in the courtroom, they are horror-stricken as the young, hard-pressed district attorney seems unable to overcome the technicalities and maneuverings that the driver\'s attorney uses to keep his client out of jail and still on the streets as a legal driver. When the judge is forced to rule time and again in favor of the defense, it appears that the driver might escape punishment altogether.',96,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOGM1MmE3NWYtZjk5Mi00MTM0LTlhZjUtYTRkNzMzMzAwZGRhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzU0NzkwMDg@.jpg',1984,'Drama, Thriller','English','Jud Taylor','William A. Schwartz, Mike Robe','Anne Hopkins, Dorothea G. Petrie, Marian Rees','Laurence Rosenthal','Robert Jessup','Paul LaMastra'),('Carbon Copy',5.6,'When a rich white corporate executive finds out that he has an illegitimate Black son, things start falling apart for him at home, at work, and in his social circles.',92,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BODAzNjkwMmQtMDA1NS00ZDMzLWJiZTYtN2NhZjg5MWY2YjUzXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDY1MDY3NjM@.jpg',1981,'Comedy, Drama','English, Spanish','Michael Schultz','Stanley Shapiro