le piece of technology--computers, planes, cars, phones, even lights--has mysteriously blacked out forever.',43,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTQ0YTIxZmUtMTVmZC00MzgxLThmYTItMDdlZjg5YmU2NzM0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjg2NjQwMDQ@.jpg',2012,'Action, Adventure, Drama, Romance, Sci-Fi, Thriller','English',NULL,'Eric Kripke, Eric Kripke, Eric Kripke',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('Kate Bush: Cloudbusting',8.4,'Music video for Kate Bush\'s song Cloudbusting about Wilhelm Reich. In 1950s Oregon, Reich and his son Peter (played by Bush) are trying to make his rainmaking machine work before the government agents arrive to arrest him.',7,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMWQ4NTRjZWItNzZmZC00ZDlkLWE2NWItYzMxMGMwOTZmMGM3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTUyODMyMw@@.jpg',1985,'Short, Biography, Drama, Music, Sci-Fi','English','Julian Doyle','Kate Bush, Terry Gilliam','Kate Bush','Kate Bush',NULL,NULL),('Heaven Help Us',6.9,'Sixteen-year-old Michael Dunn arrives at St. Basil\'s Catholic Boys School in Brooklyn circa 1965. There, he befriends all of the misfits in his class as they collide with the repressive faculty and discover the opposite sex as they come of age.',104,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzZiNDM2YzItOTVlMS00ZTg5LWE0ZDMtYmI5M2NmOWE0ZGU4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjUzOTY1NTc@.jpg',1985,'Comedy, Drama, Romance','English','Michael Dinner','Charles Purpura','Mark Carliner, Kenneth Utt, Dan Wigutow','James Horner','Miroslav Ondrícek','Stephen A. Rotter'),('Ordeal by Innocence',7.3,'Christmas 1954. Wealthy philanthropist Rachel Argyll is murdered at her family estate Sunny Point. Her adopted son Jack Argyll is arrested for her murder. He vehemently protests his innocence.',60,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2ZjNGJmMDgtODgyYy00MjNkLTk2NjUtMzRjMzQ5NjBhZmVhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjI4OTg2Njg@.jpg',2018,'Crime, Drama, Mystery, Thriller','English',NULL,'Agatha Christie, Sarah Phelps',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('Crackers',5.2,'Down-and-out Weslake (Donald Sutherland) was reduced to minding the counter at the San Francisco pawn shop of crusty Garvey (Jack Warden) when he tumbled onto a scheme by some of the boss\'s disgruntled misfit clients to rob the place. Rather than blow the whistle, however, he insinuates himself as the heist\'s mastermind. Louis Malle\'s hilarious remake of Big Deal on Madonna Street (1958) co-stars Sean Penn, Wallace Shawn, Christine Baranski, and Professor Irwin Corey.',91,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNTI0MzZmMjQtMDkyMC00NjgwLWIzYjEtYzUxMGRlN2UwMzcyXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzc5MjA3OA@@.jpg',1984,'Adventure, Comedy, Crime, Thriller','English','Louis Malle','Jeffrey Alan Fiskin','Robert Cortes, Edward Lewis','Paul Chihara','László Kovács','Suzanne Baron'),('The Winter of Our Discontent',6.7,'This story tells those self-denials of an honest man what necessary to reach his object of life.',105,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZTc4OTc0YTMtOWU3OC00OTNiLTlkMjMtYmE4ZTVlOGViZWE3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzU0NzkwMDg@.jpg',1983,'Drama','English','Waris Hussein','Michael De Guzman, John Steinbeck','Gary Adelson, R.W. Goodwin, Malcolm Stuart','Mark Snow','Robbie Greenberg','Fred A. Chulack'),('Max Dugan Returns',6.6,'Nora is a single mother who lives with her son Michael in a small house. They don\'t have much money but at least they have each other. Out of the blue comes Nora\'s father Max Dugan, who left her and her mother when Nora was nine years old. He brings a suitcase with dollar bills and showers her and Michael with gifts, trying to make up for lost time, knowing that he has a fatal heart ailment. The money comes from his shady career in Las Vegas and Nora is dating a policeman who is very interested in meeting him.',98,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2EyMTAyYWEtMzUzNi00YjYzLThmN2MtYmQzYmFlMmU5NWVhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDI4ODM5MDM@.jpg',1983,'Comedy, Drama','English','Herbert Ross','Neil Simon','Herbert Ross, Roger M. Rothstein, Neil Simon','David Shire','David M. Walsh','Richard Marks'),('A War Story',8,'Major Ben Wheeler was a Canadian doctor assigned to Singapore when the Japanese forced an unconditional surrender of the British and took him prisoner in 1942. He was taken to the notorious Kinkaseki Japanese POW mining camp in Formosa (Taiwan) and given the task of maintaining the mental and physical health of the British POWs. Wheeler kept detailed diaries of his experiences during his three and a half years at the camp and excerpts are narrated with dramatized scenes of the traumatic experiences of daily life. The working conditions in the mines caused innumerable injuries, and disease and malnutrition were rampant, but Wheeler had to make do with very few medical supplies and equipment. Also featured is newsreel footage of related events, archival footage of the camp, interviews with fellow survivors of the camp who unanimously praised Wheeler for his good work and provide their perspectives on the events described by him, and finally snippets of Wheeler\'s family life back home in Canada, before and after the war.',82,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMzBhYWQzMTUtZmZhZS00OWYwLTlhYzMtNzFhMzg4NzJkYzI2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMzU0NzkwMDg@.jpg',1981,'Drama, War','English','Anne Wheeler','Ben Wheeler, Anne Wheeler','Tom Radford, Michael J.F. Scott, Anne Wheeler','Maurice Marshall','Robert Nichol, Ron Orieux','Ray Harper'),('Threshold',7.2,'A team of experts are assembled after the U.S. Navy discovers an extra-terrestrial object briefly appeared near a ship in the Atlantic Ocean.',60,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTk3MzY4OTYzOV5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzUwMzMzMQ@@.jpg',2005,'Action, Drama, Sci-Fi, Thriller','English',NULL,'Bragi F. Schut, Bragi F. Schut, Anne McGrail',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('Eye of the Needle',7.1,'A German spy carrying information that will reveal the target of Operation Overlord becomes involved with the wife of a crippled man on an isolated island off the Scottish coast while he waits to be picked up.',112,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZjgyNjE0Y2UtNWZiMS00YzYxLWFi