, she is determined to find a way to do their part for the British war effort while avenging her brother and aims high, as God is obviously on their side: construct their own torpedo and use the converted steamboat to take out a huge German warship, the Louisa, which is hard to find or reach on the giant lake. She presses till Charlie accepts to steam up the Ulanga, brave a German fort, raging rapids, bloodthirsty parasites, and the endlessly branching river which seems to go nowhere but impenetrable swamps. Despite fierce rows and moral antagonism between a bossy devout abstentionist and a free-spirited libertine drunken loner, the two grow closer to each-other as their quest drags on.',105,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzM3YjE2NGMtODY3Zi00NTY0LWE4Y2EtMTE5YzNmM2U1NTg2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTY5Nzc4MDY@.jpg',1951,'Adventure, Drama, Romance, War','English, German, Swahili','John Huston','C.S. Forester, James Agee, John Huston, John Collier, Peter Viertel','Sam Spiegel, James Woolf, John Woolf','Allan Gray','Jack Cardiff','Ralph Kemplen'),('Sirocco',6.2,'In 1925 Damascus Harry Smith runs guns to the rebels under Emir Hassan. The French arrest him along with others and force him to sell weapons to them. He develops an interest in French intelligence officer Feroud\'s mistress Violette.',98,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTQ5MjY4MzUxNF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTgwMzUxMDM1MjE@.jpg',1951,'Action, Drama, Film-Noir, Romance, War','English, Arabic','Curtis Bernhardt','A.I. Bezzerides, Hans Jacoby, Joseph Kessel','Humphrey Bogart, Henry S. Kesler, Robert Lord','George Antheil','Burnett Guffey','Viola Lawrence'),('The Enforcer',6.7,'A threatening terrorist group called \"The People\'s Revolutionary Strike Force\" demand a ransom to be paid, otherwise they plan to blow the city apart. While Inspector \"Dirty\" Harry Callahan (Clint Eastwood) is in limbo following his unorthodox method during a robbery, he\'s sent to dispatch the terrorist group, by playing their game. This time, he has a new partner, Inspector Kate Moore (Tyne Daly), which might prove the task to be somewhat more difficult than ever, unless the two can work together.',96,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWZiZjkyNGEtYzgwMS00NjEwLTljNDYtZTExNmYzZmViNjFhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc1NTYyMjg@.jpg',1976,'Action, Crime, Thriller','English','James Fargo','Harry Julian Fink, Rita M. Fink, Stirling Silliphant, Dean Riesner, Gail Morgan Hickman, S.W. Schurr','Robert Daley','Jerry Fielding','Charles W. Short','Joel Cox, Ferris Webster'),('In a Lonely Place',7.9,'Screenwriter Dixon Steele, faced with the odious task of scripting a trashy bestseller, has hat-check girl Mildred Atkinson tell him the story in her own words. Later that night, Mildred is murdered and Steele is a prime suspect; his record of belligerence when angry and his macabre sense of humor tell against him. Fortunately, lovely neighbor Laurel Gray gives him an alibi. Laurel proves to be just what Steele needed, and their friendship ripens into love. Will suspicion, doubt, and Steele\'s inner demons come between them?',94,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNjRmZjcwZTQtYWY0ZS00ODAwLTg4YTktZDhlZDMwMTM1MGFkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNjc1NTYyMjg@.jpg',1950,'Drama, Film-Noir, Mystery, Romance, Thriller','English','Nicholas Ray','Andrew Solt, Edmund H. North, Dorothy B. Hughes','Humphrey Bogart, Henry S. Kesler, Robert Lord','George Antheil','Burnett Guffey','Viola Lawrence'),('Chain Lightning',6,'Matt Brennan runs into Jo Holloway, the Red Cross girl he romanced in Europe when he was a flyer in World War II, when he is offered a job by jet manufacturer Leland Willis as a test pilot. Carl Troxell, wants to sell an escape cockpit to the Air Force. He wants Matt to stall the presentation of JA-3 the prototype that doesn\'t include the ejection seat, to give him more time for the experimental JA-4. But Matt doesn\'t believe it is yet safe enough to try.',94,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNDI1ZTc2OWMtNjA1NC00MTA2LWJjZTgtN