rried, and returns instead with Angel. Sam, after trying to get George and Angel together, finally romances Angel, who, in the meantime, is busy fighting off the advances of George\'s younger brother, Billy. Frankie is a con man trying to steal the partners\' gold claim.',122,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BN2QyYjQ3YmYtODkxYi00Njc3LTg2ODItNjM5MjdjMzhiYmFkL2ltYWdlL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjI4MjA5MzA@.jpg',1960,'Comedy, Romance, Western','English, French','Henry Hathaway','John Lee Mahin, Martin Rackin, Claude Binyon, Ladislas Fodor, John H. Kafka, Ben Hecht, Wendell Mayes','Charles K. Feldman, Henry Hathaway, John Lee Mahin','Lionel Newman, Cyril J. Mockridge','Leon Shamroy','Dorothy Spencer'),('The Alamo',6.8,'In 1836, General Santa Anna and the Mexican Army is sweeping across Texas. To be able to stop him, General Sam Houston needs time to get his main force into shape. To buy that time he orders Colonel William Travis to defend a small mission on the Mexicans\' route at all costs. Travis\' small troop is swelled by groups accompanying Jim Bowie and Davy Crockett, but as the situation becomes ever more desperate Travis makes it clear there will be no shame if they leave while they can.',162,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZmQ1MjRmZGQtYTE1ZS00Njg4LWE4OWUtZTY2MTAwNzc3MGJlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDI2NDg0NQ@@.jpg',1960,'Adventure, Drama, History, War, Western','English, Spanish','John Wayne','James Edward Grant','James Edward Grant, John Wayne, Michael Wayne','Dimitri Tiomkin','William H. Clothier','Stuart Gilmore'),('The Horse Soldiers',7.1,'A Union Cavalry outfit is sent behind Confederate lines in strength to destroy a rail/supply center. Along with them is sent a doctor who causes instant antipathy between him and the commander. The secret plan for the mission is overheard by a southern belle who must be taken along to assure her silence. The Union officers each have different reasons for wanting to be on the mission.',120,'https://m.media-amazon.com/image