cts his nine-year-old niece, Debbie. Driven by hatred of Indians, Ethan and his young companion, Martin Pawley, ride through the unforgiving desert to track down their lost Debbie; however, is the woman they lost and the prisoner in Scar\'s teepee still the same woman the searchers seek?',119,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYWQ3YWJiMDEtMDBhNS00YjY1LTkzNmEtY2U4Njg4MjQ3YWE3XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNzkwMjQ5NzM@.jpg',1956,'Adventure, Drama, Western','English, Navajo, Spanish','John Ford','Frank S. Nugent, Alan Le May','Merian C. Cooper, Patrick Ford','Max Steiner','Winton C. Hoch','Jack Murray'),('The Conqueror',3.7,'In ancient times, the Mongolian warlord Temujin must do battle against the rival tribe that killed his father. The battles pale in comparison with Temujin\'s home life, as he attempts to woo the heart of the red-haired Tartar prisoner Bortai whom he has captured in a raid. He must also deal with various intrigues within his palace. Eventually, Bortai falls to his manly charms, Temujin defeats his enemies within and without, and is crowned Genghis Khan.',111,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZGVhMmJkZTEtZDQ4YS00N2M2LWJkNTEtNjA1NTZiM2JlYmZhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjA0MzYwMDY@.jpg',1956,'Adventure, Biography, History, Romance, War','English','Dick Powell','Oscar Millard','Howard Hughes, Dick Powell, Richard Sokolove','Victor Young','Joseph LaShelle, William E. Snyder, Leo Tover, Harry J. Wild','Robert Ford, Kennie Marstella'),('Screen Directors Playhouse',7.2,'Presented by Eastman Kodak, this show was a series of original scripts directed by acclaimed directors and featuring well-known performers. The stories ranged from musicals to comedies and dramas.',30,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWU4NTdjMmQtYmRiNC00NGU1LThkNzYtODJhZGRiMTdhMzdhXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjcyMDU4NA@@.jpg',1955,'Comedy, Drama, Romance','English',NULL,'Zoe Akins, Zoe Akins, Barbara Avedon',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('Blood Alley',6.2,'A merchant marine captain, rescued from the Chinese Communist