lish','Carl Pierson','Lindsley Parsons, Robert Emmett Tansey','Paul Malvern','Billy Barber','Archie Stout','Jerry Roberts'),('The Dawn Rider',5.1,'When John Mason\'s father is killed, John is wounded. Attracted to his nurse Alice, a conflict arises between him and his friend Ben who plans to marry Alice. John later finds the killer of his father but goes to face him not knowing Ben has removed the bullets from his gun.',53,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNzAyNzE4NTEtMTMyOC00Nzg4LWFkZWMtNjZmZWE5MGQ2ZWNkXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDMxMjQwMw@@.jpg',1935,'Western','English','Robert N. Bradbury','Lloyd Nosler, Robert N. Bradbury, Wellyn Totman','Paul Malvern',NULL,'Archie Stout','Carl Pierson'),('The Desert Trail',5.3,'Rodeo star John Scott and his gambler friend Kansas Charlie are wrongly accused of armed robbery. They leave town as fast as they can to go looking for their own suspects in Poker City.',54,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BNmJmNjg5YWQtMDA1My00Mzc4LTg5ZDAtMzFiYjA1YmY4OWNiXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMDI2NDg0NQ@@.jpg',1935,'Western','English','Lewis D. Collins','Lindsley Parsons, Lindsley Parsons','Paul Malvern','Billy Barber','Archie Stout','Carl Pierson'),('Rainbow Valley',5.3,'Rainbow Valley needs a new road and newcomer John Martin agrees to build it. Rogers is out to stop it and alters the town\'s petition to the Governor thereby obtaining the release of his boss Butch Galt. John and Butch were cell mates in prison. So Butch gets John to agree to wreck the road and furnishes him with dynamite. But dynamite is just what John needs to finish the work and he hopes to take care of Butch\'s gang at the same time.',52,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYzNlNjAwMmMtZWNkNC00ZDIzLWJjNTMtZDI5OTYyNWNlYjE2XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQwMzQ1MA@@.jpg',1935,'Western','English','Robert N. Bradbury','Lindsley Parsons, Lindsley Parsons','Paul Malvern',NULL,'William Hyer','Carl Pierson'),('Texas Terror',5.1,'Sheriff John Higgins quits and goes into prospecting after he thinks he has 