g Senator Albinius to commute his death sentence to a life of slavery. Spartacus is purchased by Batiatus for gladiator training, who promises to help him find Sura if he proves himself in training. As the series develops, the story follows the betrayals and machinations of Roman life and a tale of one man\'s heroic quest for vengeance.',55,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BZWQ4MjA2YzEtOTQzYi00NWQ1LWI0ZDEtN2VkZjhmYTc3MzU0XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyNDIzMzcwNjc@.jpg',2010,'Action, Adventure, Biography, Drama, History, Romance','English, German',NULL,'Steven S. DeKnight, Steven S. DeKnight, Aaron Helbing',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('Strangers When We Meet',7.1,'The awarded architect Larry Coe lives a boring marriage with his wife Eve Coe and their two young sons in the suburb. Larry is designing and constructing an unique house to the successful writer Roger Altar (Ernie Kovacs) on the top of a hill. Margaret \'Maggie\' Gault is a sexy blond sexually neglected by her husband Ken Gault that lives in the same neighborhood and they have a young son. When Larry meets Maggie at the bus stop of the school bus, he unsuccessfully hits on her. But soon they encounter each other again and they have a love affair. They fall in love with each other, but when their despicable neighbor Felix Anders discovers their affair, they have to decide between loyalty and respect to their families or love.',117,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYjllMTYxZjUtNTZkNi00MmNhLWFmZmItNWNmMTc0MGEyOGYwXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTQ3Njg3MQ@@.jpg',1960,'Drama, Romance','English','Richard Quine','Evan Hunter, Evan Hunter','Samuel J. Briskin, Kirk Douglas, Leo Jaffe, Richard Quine, Abe Schneider','George Duning','Charles Lang','Charles Nelson'),('The Devil\'s Disciple',7,'In a small New England town during the American War of Independence, Dick Dudgeon, a revolutionary American Puritan, is mistaken for local minister Rev. Anthony Anderson and arrested by the British. Dick discovers himself incapable of accusing another 