nd, a cellist who nearly knows her from school, seize the opportunity... A bitter woman from greater Chicago visits Virginia and confronts her past...',100,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BOGRhNGExODktNDBlNy00NGY2LWIwMzAtMGU3M2ZjNmM4NjU5L2ltYWdlL2ltYWdlXkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMTM2Mzg4MA@@.jpg',2005,'Drama, Family','English','Peter Werner','Rodney Patrick Vaccaro, Connie Willis','Gideon Amir, Desiree J. Cadena, Vince Gerardis, Ragna Nervik, Ralph Vicinanza, Robert J. Wilson, Mark Wolper','Ernest Troost','Kees Van Oostrum','Scott Vickrey'),('Blessings',6,'Released from jail after a term basically served instead of friends he refused to rat out, Charles \'Skip\' Cuddy is grateful his gentleman instinct gets him a job with living quarters as handyman on a semi-destitute estate Blessings. Working hard, he wins further confidence from the owner, bitter widow Lydia Blessing, unlike her in-living bitch nurse Jennifer. When a baby is left at the state, Skip takes it in and secretly cares for it. Lydia eventually finds out but sides with him, feeling robbed of grandchildren by her careerist only daughter Meredith. Then Skip\'s past comes knocking, and the baby\'s birth parents.',120,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BYTFlODhkNzYtNGUyYi00YWM4LWI2ZGYtN2ZlNDViNzc3YzI4XkEyXkFqcGdeQXVyMjcyMDU4NA@@.jpg',2003,'Drama','English','Arvin Brown','Anna Quindlen, Joyce Eliason','Sherri Saito, Larry Sanitsky','Roger Bellon','Thom Best','Scot J. Kelly'),('Miss Lettie and Me',5.8,'The life of a physically and emotionally isolated woman brightens considerably when her feisty grandniece visits.',100,'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/M/MV5BMTg2NjM2Mzc0OF5BMl5BanBnXkFtZTcwMzI0ODUyMQ@@.jpg',2002,'Drama','English','Ian Barry','Katherine Paterson, Dalene Young','Leah Goodman, Beth Polson, Robert Riesenberg, James A. Westman, Dalene Young','Alan Williams','William Wages','Janet Bartels-Vandagriff'),('Cheats',6,'While other kids buy into countless hours of studying just so they can get a mark i